# Sample simulation data

This folder contains small example CSV outputs generated by the simulation code.

The full research runs used much larger parameter grids. This repository includes only small sample files so the project remains easy to inspect and run.

## CSV columns

```text
delta,epsilon,final_alpha,final_alpha_prime,steps,rms

delta — dimensionless driving frequency
epsilon — dimensionless driving amplitude
final_alpha — final angular position
final_alpha_prime — final angular velocity
steps — number of integration steps
rms — RMS amplitude after transients, used to classify long-term behavior
